   - Accept if hostname is: `localhost`, ends with `.lan`, `.local`, `.internal`, `.intranet`, OR is a private IPv4 (10.x, 172.16–31.x, 192.168.x, 127.x via regex check).
   - Throw `new Error(\`Carrier REST connector URL must be a LAN-local endpoint; rejected: ${url}\`)` otherwise.
